Description: Rest on the flight into Egypt; the Virgin and Christ child sit at the base of a cherry tree; at left, Joseph reaches to pick the fruit and a bowl of cherries is on the ground. 1589 Engraving
Curator's comments: Similar to a composition by Barocci.
